data.description: Two story brick home with basement on a spacious corner lot. Ready to move in; complete with detached 1 car garage, rear shed for storage, wood stove, natural gas and central air. New gutters and down spouts. This home is definitely one to consider with great location near the fair grounds and downtown. New tall privacy fence installed around rear yard, block fence around front, wired security cameras will stay with home, plumbing and electrical update work done recently, and a new solar system has also been added (buyer must assume the solar loan in order to purchase this home - at current asking price; seller is willing to give a $15k credit at closing to assist with solar loan assumption).  Plenty of room for an additional bedroom and/or living area in the unfinished basement.  Easy to show! Must see!
